# Pergola Project Overview

## What This Is

A simple static marketing website for **KVTE Kft.**, a Hungarian woodcraft and construction business. Content is in **Hungarian (hu)**. Services include roofing, pergolas, terraces, carports, garden structures, and CNC machining.

## Tech Stack

- **HTML** — Single `index.html`, no templating or build step
- **CSS** — Vanilla CSS in `css/style.css` with CSS variables, utility classes, and responsive breakpoints
- **JavaScript** — Inline vanilla JS only; no frameworks or bundler
- **Glide.js** — Carousel via CDN (`cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@glidejs/glide`)
- **Simple Analytics** — Privacy-first analytics via `scripts.simpleanalyticscdn.com`
- **Schema.org JSON-LD** — Structured data in `<script type="application/ld+json">` for SEO

## Hosting

- **GitHub Pages** — Site is served as a static site from the repo
- **Custom domain** — `terasz-teto-minden-ami-fa.hu` (stored in `CNAME`)

## Conventions

- No npm, no build pipeline — keep it a pure static site
- Use CDNs for third-party JS/CSS; avoid local copies unless needed
- Images live in `images/`; prefer `.webp` where appropriate
- Preserve Hungarian content, meta tags, and Schema.org data when editing
